The screenshot shows a ride-hailing app interface with the title "Reserve a ride." The user has entered "Washington Hilton" in the search bar. Below the search bar, several location suggestions are listed:

1. Washington Hilton, Connecticut Avenue Northwest, Washington...
2. Hilton Washington DC National Mall, L'Enfant Plaza Southwest, Washington, DC...
3. Hilton Washington DC Capitol Hill, New Jersey Avenue Northwest, Washington...
4. Hilton Garden Inn Washington DC, 14th Street Northwest, Washington, DC, U...
5. Hilton Garden Inn Washington DC, M Street Northwest, Washington, DC, USA

There are also options to "Get more results for Washington Hi..." and "Set location on map." The top of the screen shows the time (8:53 AM) and various status icons, including battery, signal strength, and notifications.
